{"tid":2386495,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新疆烏魯木齊 警察資料庫遭泄漏，揭露針對維吾爾人大規模監控","createTime":"2021-01-29T15:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T02:15:04.000Z","uid":138409,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ea99be1924c4ef07ee79a57c2e3cdd665c398873","tid":2386495,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T15:10:39.000Z","msg":"係我知時至今日呢樣嘢已經阿媽係女人<br />\n但係篇報道幾詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未詳細睇<br />\n暫時譯住summary先<br />\n<br />\n資料庫揭露：<br />\n<br />\n- 中國官方如何從新疆穆斯林身上收集過百萬條短訊、電話聯絡人、通話記錄、網購以及銀行記錄<br />\n<br />\n- 以侵入式監控技術 尋找宗教熱誠之蛛絲馬跡（通常與極端主義劃上等號）<br />\n<br />\n- 有證據顯示「全民體檢」計劃下收集的 生物數據 輸入到 警察監控系統<br />\n<br />\n- 警察以線人收集大量烏魯木齊維吾爾人的資訊<br />\n<br />\n- 爲防止外國思想之「回流」，在國外申請庇護 可令某人被界定爲恐怖分子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/theintercept/status/1355132962153623552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftheintercept%2Fstatus%2F1355132962153623552&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH9XdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=84b62bd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftheintercept%2Fstatus%2F1355132962153623552&h=d1e6acf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/theintercept/status/1355132962153623552</a>"},{"pid":"dff84186bc9e267fa0f4edc296b4c3005526fa63","tid":2386495,"uid":367261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T15:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e468373067093b400e4ff6f086788a0d7af17eec","tid":2386495,"uid":134683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T15:12:09.000Z","msg":"好擔心部分民主國家學呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0eae09ea9b079f63a3daa328faedcafac1ae12","tid":2386495,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0